{"tid":591102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衞署醫生涉造假　親屬享長者醫療","createTime":"2018-03-13T08:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T10:06:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"686ac2d754a94953441c6bb32328c9c7e6843319","tid":591102,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:47:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180313/20330012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F20330012&d=pBSnc7Ak3Aq9zpuZKNn22kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a9f5157b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F20330012&h=43cbd3a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180313/20330012</a><br />\n<br />\n衞署醫生涉造假　親屬享長者醫療<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180313/large/13ls3p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F13ls3p4.jpg&h=8f732e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】衞生署轄下長者健康中心中年主管女醫生涉嫌於11年間偽造紀錄，包括訛稱女兒在內的4名親屬年過65歲，從而令他們可享用中心的醫療服務。涉案女醫生被控公職人員行為失當罪，昨在九龍城法院提堂，暫時毋須答辯，保釋至下月20日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訛稱4人均逾65歲<br />\n<br />\n被告女醫生徐聖智（53歲，圖），昨透過代表律師申請押後答辯，以待取得控方文件及諮詢法律意見，並獲准以2萬元保釋外出，其間不得干擾控方證人。<br />\n<br />\n控方指，衞生署在各區設立長者健康中心，只限年齡於65歲或以上的長者登記為會員，旨在縮短長者輪候醫療服務的時間。被告是案發新蒲崗長者健康中心唯一的醫生，並為主管。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指被告於2005年1月至2016年4月任職上述中心主管人員期間，在中心紀錄上作出、或導致有關職員作出虛假記項，令徐聖修、徐聖安、徐聖平及她的女兒許恩曦成為中心成員。<br />\n<br />\n她又向臨床病理化驗中心及公共衞生檢測中心人員訛稱上述4人均年屆65歲以上，符合資格接受中心提供的醫療服務及診治，令兩中心人員對4人的9個標本樣本作化驗，並向被告提交化驗報告。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC788/18<br />\n■記者楊家樂"},{"pid":"c3a97c39e605ac91f4a793e98f0076ca621e7e51","tid":591102,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:56:03.000Z","msg":"廢老不論係有冇學識都係咁乞人憎"},{"pid":"11006960cc28a1d0659468c3c4f5ad01aa0d96ce","tid":591102,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"6100ac9fe0d092805b56644c3cb73ea5a321a8b6","tid":591102,"uid":80966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:00:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77c5c79c793551e231e3f52fcc80d9d9f7134ccb","tid":591102,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"自己都未夠65，個女會大過65歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3420ec87fcad623e9cd596937417aaef7fa0f9","tid":591102,"uid":45285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:59:35.000Z","msg":"做醫生&hellip;嗰小小錢都貪&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e4527b1365b9e767ad4c81646e87992b742384","tid":591102,"uid":66501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"偷雞唔到 蝕渣米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}